Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}To be honest, this snow is really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:55.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Especially on days when headquarters issues a close patrol order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:56.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You haven't given up on Jacott-san, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:06.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, that's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:10.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You can just keep looking, and even if you can't find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:12.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...then you can still believe in the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:17.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:22.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}For a moment there, I thought you looked like Rio-senpai, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:34.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Under that cliff, at eleven o'clock. Approximately 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:56.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hang in there, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even her clothes are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata, remove her coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll switch coats with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:16.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}You actually managed to restore this facility.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:47.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}You really are the most impressive genius in the history of the academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}With that, victory is ours!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:54.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}And it's all because of you, Kannagi Noël-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They found her during patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Her left leg looks broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, her fingers are turning blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:27.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Frostbite. If we're not careful, she'll lose her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Witch of Helvetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Leave her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Looks like she'll make it through, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Her fingers are fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where's Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She wants to stay with her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's trying really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:09.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...just like how she looks when she fixes the Takemakazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:10.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She could be scouting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Of course you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No one thought we'd run into a Roman soldier ther-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is the first time I've seen a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Aren't they supposed to be our enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:43.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, I thought they would be scarier looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They probably think the same about us in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But I realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}when I saw her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:57.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}that Romans... aren't so different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, Kanata, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:00.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's almost time for the evening call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They're still arguing over the peace talks, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are we reporting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:26.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If we do, she'll be taken to the Capital and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She infiltrated enemy territory during such unstable times!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A soldier should be prepared for torture-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I will decide how to deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please give me some time, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please do not forget, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Did you meet anyone else... while carrying her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't know; I was so focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:44.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Tell me, Rio. What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A Helvetian soldier. {はるべちあの兵士.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Am I a prisoner of Helvatia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't speak Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:57.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see. {そうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So I was caught- {私わ捕れた-}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She... woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:26.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Imperial Roman Army, Tank Division, 13th Batallion Company {not sure why she said Panzer. I guess the romans are using german tanks here}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:31.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Master Sergeant Aisha Aldola, serial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:38.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Imperial Roman Army, Officer Aisha Aldola...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What was your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...serial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You have some nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How did it go? Learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seems like she doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:02.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All we know is her serial number and that her name is Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:08.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann, in charge of this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:15.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You have really nice breasts, my favorite type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Can I suck and massage them for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Can I run my fingers all over your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}W-W-What are you saying, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seems like she really doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:37.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But this is troubling. We can't interrogate her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:41.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We need find someone who speaks Roman soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:50.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Until we can interrogate her and file a report, we'll hold her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I thought I would make a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't care what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Aisha-chan, welcome to Clocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Clocktower fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes, Clocktower Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see... So I made it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:33.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, maybe it's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:56.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll eat your food because it will give me power to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She must be saying it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:09.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata's just being her usual self,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but for Noël to warm up to her is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Perhaps it's her atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:24.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Have you ever seen a fossil of an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I forgot, they don't understand me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I should have studied Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If we could communicate, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, Yumina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you have enough help shoveling snow at the Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:51.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The children are working really hard at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I guess they're growing up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:01.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}People grow as days go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Just like the sound of Kanata-san's trumpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio would say that she still has a long way to go, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, weren't you going to Treize to stock up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Things happened. That trip was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sounds like you had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I heard this terrible rumor about the Fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you for your audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The trumpet sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I didn't know there were trumpets like that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Can I play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I think Rio-senpai would allow it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a good trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Really, it's rare to see such a nice-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, that song was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Because Iliya-san's sound echoes in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and that sound echoes in Rio-senpai, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That very same song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Not only does it reverberate in Helvetia, but in Rome too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sound reverberates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In Rome and Helvetia, the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Temporary measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}"Dan...ke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah, that's right. Danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What does "danke" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It means "Thank you".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I knew they'd find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This town never bore the full brunt of the war, {lit:yaomote-bearing the full brunt of something }
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:31.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but almost everyone here lost parents, siblings, family and friends in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even if they are nice people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}to the victimes, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you remember Mikhail, the distillery owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:46.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I was at his place until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:52.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Apparently, the majority of the Helvetian Army is on the move,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}heading towards here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:01.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If that's connected to why a Roman scout is here, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}it would get blown out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:08.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Either way, we should ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Naomi-san, do you know anyone who speaks Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I am Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I am a servant of the Helvetian Orthodox Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}May a thousands blessings be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...you're a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's only one God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That greeting is blasphemous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That was just a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Enough of that. Quick ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:56.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you don't tell us, you put everyone here in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:03.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you care about them, then tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I can't tell you about my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:21.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but I wanted to see the Angel Fossil located in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She says she came to see the Angel Fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Angel Fossil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:36.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My grandmother was a maiden here at this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}"My grandmother was a maiden at this fortress."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She was captured at the Eastern Front and met my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}"She was captured at the Eastern Front and met my grandfather."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:49.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I listened to her stories as I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\i1}"I grew up listening to her stories."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:59.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So I wanted to see the Angel of the Apocalypse that brought judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:03.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}to the world in the past, the one my grandmother spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That is a mistaken doctrine! {alt: Oshie-teachings; precept; lesson; doctrine }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It was the demon that destroyed the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Leave that. Just tell us exactly what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She wanted to see the Angel of the Apocalypse that destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's why she came...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:25.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A call to advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Royal Guard Platoon... 9th Independent Mobile Division...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Ninth... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Colonel Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is he famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He's known as the Demon of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They say he revived the weapons from the ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:51.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and annihilated three towns in a single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's all right. He doesn't know that you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Regardless, you don't seem to have time to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you don't decide quickly, you'll all be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You can either hand her over-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We are Helvetian Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I lost the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I didn't make it in time, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio-senpai didn't want anyone else to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She said that that's why she's doing what she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Isn't that why she left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even then, I don't want this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're all in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:47.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}These are my orders as Commander of the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:55.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This order is by my own judgment. I will take full responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you all understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:13.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I am Commander of the 1121st Platoon, Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:17.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Several days ago, a Roman scout was captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:23.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Unfortunately, due to an accident during questioning... we couldn't confirm some details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:29.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Coincidentally, we've received information from a witness that a Roman soldier is in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Does this ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}As of this moment, the 1121st Fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}is under the control of the 9th Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't raise your voice so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:02.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Aisha-san just told me about the legend of the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's strange... but according to her-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:09.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:11.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Search there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Nothing over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:13.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She has to be here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Tighten security!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:35.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She said that she hasn't asked for your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:39.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noël... Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're the Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:00.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noël-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:19.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is the 1121st Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:26.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A large contingent of Roman soldiers has appeared at the Seize's border, in Nomansland?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.30,0:24:20.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Next time: Resound in the Blue Skies
